[SN]TITLE[SN]
Rob Hunt: Brighton defender joins Oldham Athletic on loan

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
League One side Oldham Athletic have signed Brighton defender Rob Hunt on loan until the end of the season.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 21-year-old full-back has progressed through the Seagulls' youth academy and made his first-team debut in the EFL Cup in August.
Brighton boss Chris Hughton said he wanted Hunt to go out on loan when he signed a new deal in October.
He is eligible to make his debut for the Latics against Bradford City at Boundary Park on Saturday.
